headline: DS Smith Drypack Solution Benefits Seafood Industry
summary: ATLANTA, March 11, 2025--DS Smith, a leading fiber-based packaging manufacturer, which was acquired by International Paper in 2025, is helping seafood processors reduce costs and CO2 emissions through its DryPack seafood box. DryPack is a 100% water-resistant, box that, when packed with ice, can keep fresh fish below 40 degrees Fahrenheit for over 40 hours in cold chain operations.
